I"x<p>“Role Models is a 2008 American comedy film directed by David Wain about two energy drink salesmen who are ordered to perform 150 hours of community service as punishment for various offenses. For their service, the two men work at a program designed to pair kids with adult role models. The film stars Seann William Scott, Paul Rudd, Christopher Mintz-Plasse, Bobb’e J. Thompson, Jane Lynch, and Elizabeth Banks.” - http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Role_models</p>

<p>If you’re looking for another dumb movie with cheap laughs, you’ve found one.</p>

<p>4/10, mainly due to the redeeming feature that is Jane Lynch.</p>
